        <page n="01" image="va.au.rv.1863.08.14.01">
            <div type="a">
                <column>5</column>
                <head>Pull Together</head>
                <origin>Virginian</origin>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>Calls on Southerners to pull together in unity and spirit, encourages those
                    in the service to rally to their duty, and encourages those who have deserted to
                    rally to the calls of President Davis and General Lee to return to their
                    stations.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
            <pageNote>This page also has war news and advertisements.</pageNote>
        </page>
        <page n="02" image="va.au.rv.1863.08.14.02">
            <div type="a">
                <column>2</column>
                <head>Let Us Be Just</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names/>
                <summary>The editor encourages readers to support President Davis and the army
                    officers he has appointed instead of second guessing them after the defeat of
                    Vicksburg.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look>**</look>
            </div>
            <div type="a">
